Elizabeth Baur https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elizabeth_Baur 0 Elizabeth Baur (December 1, 1947 – September 30, 2017) was an American actress. She is perhaps best known for her roles as Teresa O'Brien on the CBS western series, Lancer, with Andrew Duggan, James Stacy, Wayne Maunder, and Paul Brinegar, and as Officer Fran Belding on NBC's crime drama series Ironside.
